title: MisterMusic Show 306 indie,alternative,rock Radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 306  [2 hours] 192 kbps MP3 stereo-



Time for a new month, and a new MisterMusic show!

On this week's show new music by Wolf Alice and a new track from Bob Mould from his latest album.
Plus a big hit that scored a number 1 spot on the US modern rock chart in early June 1990 is this week's 'Oldie of the Week'.

Playing classic hits from the past in a mix of new indie and alternative rock, it's the MisterMusic Show.




The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
